entry.title: TobBrandt/vector-instances-collections
entry.summary: This package defines instances of the Foldable, Unfoldable, Collection, Sequence and Indexed classes from Data.Collections for all pure Vector types (those found in Data.Vector, Data.Vector.Unboxed, Data.Vector.Primitive, Data.Vector.Storable).
